//Design of Comment Class
Class : Comment 
Attributes:
*_person : string
*_text : string

Constructors:
Comment()
Comment(person : string, text : string)

//Design of Video Class
Class : Video
Attributes:
*_title : string
*_author : string
*_length : int
*comments : List<Comment>

Constructors:
*Video(title : string, author : string, length : int)

Behaviors:
*AddComment(comment : Comment) : void
*GetNumberOfComments() : int
*GetComments() : List<Comment>